OL,3,CLeader of Jersey's largest political
OL,4,Cparty loses seat
OL,6,FThe head of Jersey's largest political
OL,7,Fparty, Sam Mezec, has lost his seat.
OL,9,FReform Jersey's leader came 10th in
OL,10,Fthe race to become Senator in an
OL,11,Fisland-wide poll.
OL,13,FOnly the top nine are elected, meaning
OL,14,FMezec misses out by just one place.
OL,16,FDespite securing a large proportion of
OL,17,Fthe votes in St Helier, he failed to
OL,18,Fsecure enough support of the
OL,19,Felectorate elsewhere - particularly in
OL,20,Fthe more rural parishes.
