OL,3,CLeader of Jersey's largest political
OL,4,Cparty loses seat
OL,6,FIt seems likely that deputy leader
OL,7,FLyndsay Feltham will assume control of
OL,8,Fthe party.
OL,10,FHowever, she still faces a fight to
OL,11,Fretain her own seat as a Deputy of St
OL,12,FHelier Central - with the result
OL,13,Fexpected later on Monday (8 June).
